    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Use with reference to the period c.1250 to as late as 1500 where the terms "Gothic (Medieval)" or "Late Gothic" are not appropriate.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
